## Revenue Analysis

### Monthly Revenue Trend

Revenue grew from September through October, with October recording the peak. November saw a slight decrease due to orders entering Processing and Pending status rather than completing as Delivered.

| Month | Transactions | Revenue | Avg Sale |
|---|---|---|---|
| September 2024 | 6 | £782.92 | £130.49 |
| October 2024 | 7 | £1,109.92 | £158.56 |
| November 2024 | 7 | £824.84 | £117.83 |
| **TOTAL** | **20** | **£2,717.68** | **£135.88** |

October was the strongest month — **41% above the September baseline**.

