## Recommendations

### Immediate Actions (This Week)
- Contact the **3 Critical and High risk customers** with targeted discount offers to prevent further churn
- Confirm restock order for **Standing Desk (Electric)** — current stock 18 units, high sell-through rate
- Assign dedicated account management to the **2 Platinum customers**

### Medium Term Actions (Next 30 Days)
- Launch a **Bronze-to-Silver upgrade campaign** — double points month for the 5 Bronze customers
- Investigate the **November fulfilment bottleneck** — 3 orders stuck in Processing/Pending at month end
- Expand the **Electronics catalogue** — highest average order value per transaction

### Strategic Actions (Next Quarter)
- Set a target to move **3 Silver customers** to Gold tier through the loyalty programme
- Introduce a **product bundling strategy** combining Electronics + Accessories (e.g. Headphones + Charging Pad)
- Build a proper **ML churn model** once the dataset reaches 100+ customer records

